{"id":28095495442,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAGip89Eg","head_branch":"perf-geofeatures-geometry-prefilter","head_sha":"6fe57bcbb6214d00e1ac3c938243b435dcd41e4b","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54328,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":75783110796,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAARpQaAjA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442","pull_requests":[{"id":3927270702,"number":24279,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24279","head":{"ref":"perf-geofeatures-geometry-prefilter","sha":"f2d66182e47aee0b763173d2ccedb431a28e2dc4","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"a03204cbccd2096dcd34cd8e19e8f0ac6981bc3b","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-06-24T11:33:34Z","updated_at":"2026-06-24T11:42:15Z","run_started_at":"2026-06-24T11:33:34Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/75783110796","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28095495442/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry\n\ngeoFeatures resolves the `ou` dimension into full OrganisationUnit\nentities, then discards every unit without geometry in-memory. On a\nlarge hierarchy (Nigeria prod: ~255k level-5 units, all null-geometry)\nthis hydrates a quarter-million entities — ~7.6s CPU and ~4.7 GB\nallocated — only to return [].\n\nThread an optional `geometryOnly` flag from DataQueryRequest through\nDimensionalObjectProvider and OrganisationUnitService down to\nHibernateOrganisationUnitStore, which appends `and o.geometry is not\nnull`. Default off, so all other callers dispatch the original 2-arg\nmethods unchanged. Skipped in geoJsonAttribute (coordinateField) mode,\nwhere coordinates come from an attribute and the geometry column may be\nnull. The in-memory filter remains the precise final gate.\n\nWhen the geometry-filtered resolution is empty, the E7143 empty-dimension\nguard is suppressed so geoFeatures still returns 200 [] rather than an\nerror.\n\nValidated on production (Nigeria, deployed on 2.40): a comparable\nhigh-level layer dropped from ~8.6s/4.7GB to 14ms/747KB.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"6fe57bcbb6214d00e1ac3c938243b435dcd41e4b","tree_id":"66c0d1c4d0a6e6758d8485a3297ca557b091a2b1","timestamp":"2026-06-24T11:33:09Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gi